Title : Tore O. Vorren
Text : {{Orphan|date=June 2016}}

'''Tore Ola Vorren''' (17 April 1944 – 16 June 2013) was a [[Norway|Norwegian]] geologist.

He took the [[cand.real.]] degree in 1970 at the [[University of Bergen]]. He was appointed as a lecturer at the [[University of Tromsø]] in 1973, took the [[dr.philos.]] degree here in 1978 and was promoted to a professor in 1979. He served as both [[dean (academic)|dean]] and prorector there, and chairman of the [[University Centre in Svalbard]]. He was a fellow of the [[Norwegian Academy of Science and Letters]] from 1993.<ref name=50y>{{cite news|title=50 år|last=Lippestad|first=Jenny|date=19 April 1994|work=Nordlys|page=|language=Norwegian}}</ref><ref name=obit>{{cite news|title=Tore O. Vorren til minne|last=Hald|first=Morten|author2=Mienert, Jürgen |date=2 July 2013|work=Nordlys|page=44|language=Norwegian}}</ref>

